{"id": 1479, "genre": 1001, "title": "过年回家，你发现你们那儿都发生了什么变化？", "description": "你的家乡现在是什么模样？来聊聊你的回乡见闻。（题图来自：Pawel Mildner）", "record_count": 5311, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170125175136Alk0pt5GE9QaJ4gZ.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-01-31T17:00:46Z", "options": [{"id": 160256, "content": "我竟然变大了一岁", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 507236}, {"id": 160512, "content": "有网吧了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896039}, {"id": 161024, "content": "小县城都有美团外卖了！", "image": "img/option/option/20170203105135VxrgM5ZDn2QquUYI.png", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923010}, {"id": 160257, "content": "Blued上附近有人?", "image": null, "praise_count": 211, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 668809}, {"id": 161025, "content": "过年的种种无以名状的小情绪，所有想说的，上面都说到了。\r\n10:46AM，2017.02.03", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 2362}, {"id": 160258, "content": "爸爸妈妈老了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 612940}, {"id": 173058, "content": "小时候玩的地方，全部推掉盖成房子了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 953835}, {"id": 160259, "content": "朋友的聚的机会不多啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919854}, {"id": 160515, "content": "死了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 896039}, {"id": 160260, "content": "小镇电影院太火了，屈臣氏也开了", "image": null, "praise_count": 64, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 475237}, {"id": 160772, "content": "已经在现在的城市定居了", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 814564}, {"id": 160261, "content": "没人短信拜年，都是微信红包", "image": null, "praise_count": 99, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 645829}, {"id": 160262, "content": "爷爷奶奶在去年先后去世，过年没有年夜饭可吃了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 504390}, {"id": 160263, "content": "逼婚的父母越来越多了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 691469}, {"id": 160775, "content": "所有人的脾气都不是很好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796044}, {"id": 163591, "content": "过年出门成了我跟爸爸的事情，也突然发现小时候的异性小伙伴们都长成了帅气高大的模样", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929105}, {"id": 167175, "content": "我爸妈竟然下支付宝还嘀嘀打车了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 937694}, {"id": 160776, "content": "都去别的地方玩了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 796044}, {"id": 163080, "content": "自己變胖了?", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927089}, {"id": 160777, "content": "这次居然没走什么亲戚", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915794}, {"id": 161033, "content": "没有炮竹声，想起小时候简直天天在外面放鞭炮。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 915344}, {"id": 180233, "content": "没什么年味了  东西也不好吃了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 962224}, {"id": 160522, "content": "以往，?现车", "image": "img/option/option/20170201203034rjSEG4c6opWBMnfm", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921394}, {"id": 162570, "content": "再也没有长长的一排灯会了，也没有以前那样放炮的热闹了，这个年真冷啊。明明，去年还是很热闹很热闹的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 365084}, {"id": 163082, "content": "今年春晚又没看！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 927379}, {"id": 160267, "content": "我还有压岁钱可以拿", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920600}, {"id": 164363, "content": "家里的新房子造好啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 930735}, {"id": 166411, "content": "居然不让放炮了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 935429}, {"id": 168715, "content": "没变化", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940869}, {"id": 168716, "content": "正月十六早起烤火的人都不想以前一样在自家门口了，扭头就能看见一长龙的火堆，都改自己家了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 940869}, {"id": 160269, "content": "村里人生活的确变好了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719410}, {"id": 160525, "content": "人越来越现实了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921485}, {"id": 160270, "content": "糖没人吃了，婴儿多了，全都问啥时候结婚了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 874199}, {"id": 161550, "content": "东北天气变暖了\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 909807}, {"id": 166670, "content": "堵车是因为宝骏和哈弗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 199977}, {"id": 160271, "content": "烦烦烦 不就27岁了么  ", "image": null, "praise_count": 26, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 315666}, {"id": 163855, "content": "听我妈说有更多人开始吸毒了，担忧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 305652}, {"id": 160272, "content": "霾更大了", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920915}, {"id": 160528, "content": "不爱吃饺子了，也吃不动饺子了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 919744}, {"id": 161040, "content": "超市里有微信支付了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 910583}, {"id": 160273, "content": "回家后家里人之间各种闹掰，过年成冷战", "image": null, "praise_count": 20, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 820074}, {"id": 161297, "content": "感觉年味又淡了就是真的", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923808}, {"id": 160530, "content": "有人跳广场舞了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 695563}, {"id": 160786, "content": "长大，过年没有年味。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 922196}, {"id": 170258, "content": "都在聚，聚在一起吃……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 898700}, {"id": 160275, "content": "年夜饭改到餐馆吃了", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 920921}, {"id": 161299, "content": "以前觉着这座城市很大很丰富，现在却觉着很小很无聊", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 923801}, {"id": 160276, "content": "北京的外地人和车并没有少", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 913058}, {"id": 163860, "content": "感觉这个世道变了个样，都不像以前那个小村子了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 929681}, {"id": 160789, "content": "我们镇上堵车，村里门口基本都会有辆车", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921837}]}